title: Art Garfunkel - Breakaway (1975 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-
description:
Art Garfunkel - Breakaway (1975 quad/surround mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 DTS @ 1536kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.

Converted from quad SQ encoded vinyl using a FOSGATE RESEARCH TATE II 101A hardware decoder.
 
 
"Expensively produced but chilly artifacts from the choirboy half of the immortal duo. "Breakaway" was a 1976 hit single (it's Gallagher and Lyle's song, not the Beach Boys'), and it also includes the Simon and Garfunkel reunion song, "My little Town"." **
- Dave Marsh, Rolling Stone
